  • Field Details

    • MAX_QUEUE_WAIT_DEFAULT

      public static final int MAX_QUEUE_WAIT_DEFAULT
      Defines a maximum time in milliseconds that a connection request could wait in the connection queue. After this period expires, an exception will be thrown in the calling method.
